hopobject.body: Your cash is being counted lgm pharmaceuticals inc We all know Hollywood is a bit Twitter-happy, so we've rounded up the hottest, cutest, funniest and just plain wackiest celebrity Twitpics. Enjoy ... It's the future Mrs. Levine! Victoria's Secret Angel Behati Prinsloo -- and Adam Levine's new fiancee -- isn't afraid to bare some skin.
